 receiver.\nFinally, we present a few possible defenses, such as installing noise filters,\nand discuss their limitations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 18 Jan 2020 21:18:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 27 Jan 2020 20:16:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-29"}
