tions are linear on the number of variables of the\nmodel.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 19 Jan 2020 00:53:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 30 Apr 2021 16:45:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-03"}
