ysis and an elementary model based on a quantum theory of\nradiation-matter interaction. Our results suggest a new approach to study\nexciton-polaritons and pave the way towards large-scale and low-cost integrated\npolaritonic devices operating at room temperature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 19 Jan 2020 10:09:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-22"}
