 for power utility companies. The\nproposed method is validated via case studies of IEEE 39-bus and 118-bus test\nsystems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 19 Jan 2020 15:35:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 5 Jul 2020 06:20:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-07"}
